As for documentation, the student must develop a user's guide with the main screens
of the system, showing with clarity the usability of the software. We don't require a specific format for the
elaboration, although direct and dynamic language is important. Here are some tips:
Use ABNT rules;
Use arrows and explanatory shapes;
Documentation must include at least the following items: Introduction - Development and
Conclusion;
Extra activity (not compulsory): class and use case diagrams of the system (content worked on
in Software Analysis).
